wc sample.txt
    1      16      74 sample.txt
-----------------------------------
STEPS
	read options/filenames
		process.argv => filenames & options
	process word,line,char counts
		split by newline, split by non-words, find length
	display results
		formatted output by each requested option
-----------------------------------
Cases
	wc sample.txt
	wc -l sample.txt
	wc -c sample.txt
	wc -w sample.txt
-----------------------------------